ecipient_username";s:6:"Ashley";s:4:"text";s:106:"And no one else seems to have a problem with it. Most just want a chance to say goodbye before he passes. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420351142";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f033f9";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203511441";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f738d5";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1191859;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1191859";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"71";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Ashley";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"189";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:2:"20";s:18:"recipient_username";s:6:"Jester";s:4:"text";s:177:"Yeah well nobody else active is playing his ~kid~. And honestly I think people DO have a problem with it but they either don&#039;t have will to argue about or are just too lazy";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420351216";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#8808f7";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203512276";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b252f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1191860;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1191860";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"71";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Ashley";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"189";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:5:"10852";s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Scarlet";s:4:"text";s:40:"/me sighs. He still wants to kill Jester";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420351225";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#8808f7";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203512342";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b252f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1191867;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1191867";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Scarlet";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"51";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:6:"Ashley";s:4:"text";s:226:"I&#039;m well aware of Jester&#039;s intentions. And while yes it does upset me too he does have a right to decide things that happen to his character up to a point. I take it you&#039;ve been trying to persuade him otherwise?";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420351448";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f00707";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203514489";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f77676";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1191872;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1191872";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"71";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Ashley";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"189";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:5:"10852";s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Scarlet";s:4:"text";s:311:"Yes. Characters don&#039;t exist in a vacuum. Pointlessly dropping them off cliffs doesn&#039;t do anything but hurt other people&#039;s characters. Honestly I wouldn&#039;t have a problem with it if it had some kind of roleplay value, but it&#039;s just a sudden death out of, honestly, sheer [i]laziness[/i]. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420351566";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#8808f7";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203515773";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b252f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1191875;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1191875";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Scarlet";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"51";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:6:"Ashley";s:4:"text";s:241:"Death also happens suddenly and with out warning or much of a warning. Take my father-in-law for instance, earlier last year he suffered a cardiac arrest and the only clue we had was heart burn and mild chest pain that lasted for him a week.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420351679";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f00707";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203516793";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f77676";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1191879;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1191879";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"71";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Ashley";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"189";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:5:"10852";s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Scarlet";s:4:"text";s:58:"This is not the real world. That&#039;s kind of the point.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420351715";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#8808f7";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203517265";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b252f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1191885;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1191885";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Scarlet";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"51";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:6:"Ashley";s:4:"text";s:101:"So then what are you asking me to do? Tell him he can&#039;t die because you don&#039;t want him too?";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420351764";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f00707";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203517647";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f77676";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1191888;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1191888";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"71";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Ashley";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"189";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:5:"10852";s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Scarlet";s:4:"text";s:260:"I don&#039;t know, honestly. I just don&#039;t understand how nobody else gives a **** that he&#039;s doing this. Now I get to be shoved into either not getting to play Ashley or having to do this ridiculous depressing **** because Jester feels like being lazy";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420351826";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#8808f7";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203518381";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b252f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1191890;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1191890";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"71";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Ashley";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"189";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:5:"10852";s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Scarlet";s:4:"text";s:126:"I&#039;m not complaining to you as a guide, I&#039;m complaining to you as someone else closely tied to Jester as a character.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420351908";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#8808f7";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203519193";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b252f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1191895;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1191895";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"71";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Ashley";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"189";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:2:"20";s:18:"recipient_username";s:6:"Jester";s:4:"text";s:258:"I understand it&#039;s your character and your decision, so no, I can&#039;t really stop you. I just really think you should consider that this is a really selfish way to go about it, and I think you&#039;ll find it&#039;s really unsatisfying once you do it.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420352049";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#8808f7";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203520608";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b252f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1191896;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1191896";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Scarlet";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"51";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:6:"Ashley";s:4:"text";s:49:"Thank you for the clarification on that last part";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420352054";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f00707";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203520518";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f77676";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1191898;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1191898";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Scarlet";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"51";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:6:"Ashley";s:4:"text";s:181:"And yes I personally feel it hurts and for me it&#039;s because of that recent loss in my life... this echos it somewhat and I don&#039;t like the idea of revisiting those emotions.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420352085";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f00707";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203520850";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f77676";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1191899;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1191899";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Scarlet";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"51";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:6:"Ashley";s:4:"text";s:85:"And seeing Ashley&#039;s pain in this really reminds me of it more than anything else";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420352116";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f00707";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203521159";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f77676";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1191912;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1191912";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"71";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Ashley";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"189";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:5:"10852";s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Scarlet";s:4:"text";s:110:"And the thing isn&#039;t just those emotions. It&#039;s that those emotions are being brought up for ~nothing~";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420352312";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#8808f7";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203523233";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b252f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1191913;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1191913";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"71";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Ashley";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"189";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:5:"10852";s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Scarlet";s:4:"text";s:96:"There&#039;s no buildup to killing Jester like this. Nothing led to it. Nothing is led to by it.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420352327";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#8808f7";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203523387";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b252f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1191915;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1191915";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"71";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Ashley";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"189";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:5:"10852";s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Scarlet";s:4:"text";s:54:"So it&#039;s not just pain but it&#039;s needless pain";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420352341";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#8808f7";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203523522";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b252f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1191927;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1191927";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Scarlet";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"51";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:6:"Ashley";s:4:"text";s:282:"I echoed to him some of what you just told me as they were fair points to make and I agree with them on a personal level. I even told him that I agreed them on a personal level and that not to regard them as a message from a guide. He seems upset and now is talking about reconing. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420353100";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f00707";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203531000";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f77676";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1191928;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1191928";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Scarlet";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"51";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:6:"Ashley";s:4:"text";s:253:"My biggest point to make was to showcase to him how he spent... well literally months under the radar and did not interact with anyone of us IC ... Then suddenly this death business came &quot;out of the blue&quot;? It sparked a lot of us to learn more.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420353196";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f00707";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203531959";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f77676";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}}